title Create New Note

browser->server: HTTP GET https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/notes
server-->browser: webpage
note over  browser: User enters new note and hits the save button
browser->server:  Form submit request HTTP POST https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/new_note
server-->browser: 302 URL redirect
note left of browser: Sever rediects to notes page
browser->server:  HTTP GET https:browser->server: HTTP GET https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/notes
server-->browser: HTML-code
browser->server: HTTP GET https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/main.css
server-->browser: main.css
browser->server: HTTP GET https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/main.js
server-->browser: main.js

note over browser:
browser starts executing js-code
that requests JSON data from server 
end note//fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/notes



